Product.Description:
&lt;p&gt;A whole Muntjac, cut to order. By ordering a whole deer for your freezer, you will not only ensure a significant supply of venison, but we will send you a certificate telling you which of our highly trained hunters shot the deer, where it was shot, and when, giving you the ultimate in provenance!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A field dressed Muntjac, might typically weigh in at around 10 kilos &amp;ndash; for which you can expect to pay around &amp;pound;10 per kilo. Depending on how you choose to have your deer cut, you should expect to lose around a third of the un-cut weight &amp;ndash; but what you keep remains exceptional value and beautifully butchered.&lt;/p&gt;
